Gikou
------------------------------------------
Shogi software Gikou

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.10-1
  libgomp1-14.4.0-1
  libstdc++6-14.4.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-14.4.0-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/gikou-official/Gikou

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/gikou-official/Gikou/archive/refs/tags/v2.0.2.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack Gikou-2.0.2-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./Gikou-2.0.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/Gikou-2.0.2-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/Gikou-2.0.2-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(Gikou)
  /usr/bin/Gikou.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/Gikou.README
  /usr/share/doc/Gikou/Copying.txt
  /usr/share/doc/Gikou/README.md
  /usr/share/doc/Gikou/gikou_ja.txt

------------------

